\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces  Architecture of the MZSGO framework. The pipeline comprises four integrated stages: (1) multi-modal feature projection; (2) protein modality dropout during training, where dashed lines (with red crosses) indicate the stochastic discarding of protein features with a probability of p=0.15, while solid lines represent preserved modalities; (3) a gated fusion module for adaptive feature integration; (4) a binary classification head for GO function prediction.}}{3}{figure.caption.1}\protected@file@percent }
